HTML:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSS Level 1</title>
    <link rel ="stylesheet" href ="css.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>I'm reading a novel</h1>
    <h2>This is a heading</h2>
    <h2 id="heading">This is customized</h2>
    <h2 class="myclass">This is class in heading</h2>
    <p class="myclass">This is class in paragraph</p>
    <button>Click me</button>
</body>
</html>

CSS:
* {
    color:blue;
}

h1{
    color:green;
}

button{
    color:brown;
}

#heading{
    color:blueviolet;
}

.myclass{
    color:crimson;
}
